item.title: Please help
item.dc:creator: @bloodbath32 bloodbath32
item.description:
@bloodbath32 wrote:

Right click your compiler and click edit and change it to this

@echo off title YOURSERVNAME Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_07\bin/java.exe" server pause

And change the jre1.5.0_07 and jdk1.5.0_07 depending on what JRE and JDK you’ve got. If you have 08 change 07 to 08.
